<br>
For more, here's a link telling how much is paid for which job:<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.skillsnet.net/occguide/salary-anim.cfm">www.skillsnet.net/occguide/salary-anim.cfm</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
